      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 78,
      "message": "Yes we should create a bean or use static as I stated in my previus commecnt into solution section. Creating bean would be more cleaner/appropriate way like below: \n\nStep 1 : Add ObjectMapper and  JsonObjectMapper into spring test context\n\n@SpringBootTest(classes = [ObjectMapper, JsonObjectMapper,...\n\nStep 2 : Inject JsonObjectMapper object that would wire ObjectMapper object from spring test context\n\n@Autowired\nprivate JsonObjectMapper jsonObjectMapper;",
